{
  "texts": [
    "Besides, we also report the performance of GPT-3.5 [1] and GPT-4 [3] as a reference.",
    "Since NWGI cannot be measured using GPT-3.5/4 [83], we report the averaged metric of the first three and four evaluation datasets for an overall comparison.Experimental results.",
    "Table 5 shows the accuracy and F1 score comparisons among various models.From the table, we see that (1) FedAvg [20] significantly and consistently outperforms local training.",
    "Specifically, on average (Avg:4), FedAvg outperforms local training by 11.5% relatively.",
    "(2) On average, SCAFFOLD [50], FedAvgM [44], and FedAdaGrad [54] are three FL algorithms that have better performance in this financial domain."
  ]
}